      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/nordea-earnings-meet-estimates-as-net-interest-income-has-peaked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北欧联合银行 (Nordea Bank Abp) 表示将在明年初进行新一轮股票回购，这让一些原本预计今年将获得新资本回报的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
